<br>
I personally, managed to get my book from Severilous and am in the process of attempting to get Thraax his book.<br>
<br>
I do have a Naggy raid scheduled for 4 May 03,  and if the book does not drop.  in a few weeks,  I will be scheduling one again, and again and again.  until Thraax and others of the Utopian Guard get their epic items.<br>
<br>
At the same time,  I am checking all the zones that have other dragons,  it Talendor, Severilous, Gorenaire, etc. <br>
<br>
But this time,  I must agree with Madsum,  he has not scheduled the raid twice in a row.  It is an open raid as well,  so do what all the others that are after their epic pieces do,  show up,  help out, and hope that you win the roll.  Or else,  sit up until the time comes to post a reservation,  and be the first.<br>
<br>
Nerak... <br>
