<br>
So, you schedule your one allowed Naggy/Vox raid once a month...the item you need (scale/book) doesn't drop.  Well hells bells...you gotta stick at 52 for another month.  Umm...I think not.<br>
<br>
I do have to wonder why Xiaro is making such an issue about this if he has no desire for Naggy or Vox.  /shrug - just like tootsie pops, the world may never know.<br>
